  "detailed_description": "Efemeris is an online boardgame dedicated to 2 players, select your nation, captains and crew members and explore the Celestial Vault!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring your turn you have 4 phases to execute:<br />\r\n - Exploring plhase<br />\r\n - Collecting phase<br />\r\n - Tactical phase<br />\r\n - Construciton phase<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe first nation who conquer 5 planets, win the game instantatly!<br />\r\nYou can play online against the world or against CPU, start a party, join the lobby and conquer the Celestial Vault!",
  "about_the_game": "Efemeris is an online boardgame dedicated to 2 players, select your nation, captains and crew members and explore the Celestial Vault!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring your turn you have 4 phases to execute:<br />\r\n - Exploring plhase<br />\r\n - Collecting phase<br />\r\n - Tactical phase<br />\r\n - Construciton phase<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe first nation who conquer 5 planets, win the game instantatly!<br />\r\nYou can play online against the world or against CPU, start a party, join the lobby and conquer the Celestial Vault!",
